Symbol.Script_3D:
! Fuel Tank
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- TANK --- !
ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 ROTy 90 CYLIND dTWidth, dTDepth/2 CUTPOLYA 2, 2, 0, 0, 0, 913, dTDepth/2, 360, 4013 DEL 2
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ADDz legHeight+dTDepth/2 CYLIND dTDepth/2+upperOpeningHeight-openingCapHeight, openingRadius ADDz dTDepth/2+upperOpeningHeight-openingCapHeight CYLIND openingCapHeight, openingRadius*1.2 DEL 2 ELSE ADDz legHeight+dTDepth/2 CYLIND dTDepth/2+upperOpeningHeight, openingRadius DEL 1 ENDIF
IF Constatus_1 THEN ADD ConPosX_1, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, dTDepth/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_1/2, 360, 4001 DEL 1 ENDIF
IF Constatus_2 THEN ADD ConPosX_2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, dTDepth/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_2/2, 360, 4001 DEL 1 ENDIF
IF Constatus_3 THEN ADD ConPosX_3, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, dTDepth/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_3/2, 360, 4001 DEL 1 ENDIF
IF Constatus_4 THEN ADD ConPosX_4, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, dTDepth/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_4/2, 360, 4001 DEL 1 ENDIF
IF Constatus_5 THEN ADD ConPosX_5, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, dTDepth/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_5/2, 360, 4001 DEL 1 ENDIF
IF Constatus_6 THEN ADD ConPosX_6, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, dTDepth/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_6/2, 360, 4001 DEL 1 ENDIF
IF Constatus_7 THEN ADD ConPosX_7, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, dTDepth/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_7/2, 360, 4001 DEL 1 ENDIF
CUTEND
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN RESOL res/2 ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight TUBE 2, 5, 1+2+16+32, 0, 0, 901, sideTubeRadius, 360, 4001,
1, 0, 0.075, 0, 0, 0, 0.075, 0, -sideTubeDist, 0, 0.075, 0, -sideTubeDist, 0, dTDepth, 0, -sideTubeDist, 0, dTDepth+1, 0 DEL 1
ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth-0.095 ROTy -90 CYLIND sideTubeDist, sideTubeRadius DEL 2 RESOL res ELSE ADD -dTWidth/2-sideTubeDist-sideTubeRadius, -sideTubeRadius, legHeight+0.075-sideTubeRadius BLOCK sideTubeDist+sideTubeRadius, sideTubeRadius*2, dTDepth-0.075+sideTubeRadius DEL 1 ENDIF
! --- SUPPORT --- !
num = INT((dTWidth-0.30*ww-0.15*dd)/1.20) IF num < EPS THEN num = 1 IF num > 3 THEN num = 3
FOR p = 1 TO num+1 ADDx -dTWidth/2+0.15*ww+((dTWidth-0.30*ww-0.15*dd)/(num))*(p-1) ROTz 90 CALL "MEP_m_Tank_support_4" PARAMETERS supLen = 0.15*dd, supHeight = legHeight+dTDepth/4, supThick = 0.035, footWidth = dTDepth+0.08*dd, footThick = 0.035, tankDia = dTDepth, tankDeepening = dTDepth/4, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, supMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, res = res, hptsID = 200*p DEL 2 NEXT p

Symbol.Script_2D:
! Fuel Tank
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2-sideTubeDist-sideTubeRadius, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -dTWidth/2, -sideTubeRadius, 1, -dTWidth/2-sideTubeDist, -sideTubeRadius, 1, -dTWidth/2-sideTubeDist, sideTubeRadius, 1001, -dTWidth/2, sideTubeRadius, 1, -dTWidth/2, -sideTubeRadius, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
ARC2 -dTWidth/2-sideTubeDist, 0, sideTubeRadius, -90, 90
CIRCLE2 0, 0, openingRadius
! --- SUPPORT --- !
num = INT((dTWidth-0.30*ww-0.15*dd)/1.20) IF num < EPS THEN num = 1 IF num > 3 THEN num = 3
FOR p = 1 TO num+1 ADD2 -dTWidth/2+0.15*ww+((dTWidth-0.30*ww-0.15*dd)/(num))*(p-1), 0 ROT2 90 CALL "MEP_m_Tank_support_4" PARAMETERS supLen = 0.15*dd, supHeight = legHeight+dTDepth/4, supThick = 0.035, footWidth = dTDepth+0.08*dd, footThick = 0.035, tankDia = dTDepth, tankDeepening = dTDepth/4, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, supMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_pen = gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen = gs_back_pen, gs_fill_type = gs_fill_type, hptsID = 200*p DEL 2 NEXT p ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 2, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 2, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 2, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConPosZ_4=ConPosZ_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConEdit_4 = 2, ConPosX_5=ConPosX_5, ConPosY_5=ConPosY_5, ConPosZ_5=ConPosZ_5, ConLength_5=ConLength_5, ConEdit_5 = 2, ConPosX_6=ConPosX_6, ConPosY_6=ConPosY_6, ConPosZ_6=ConPosZ_6, ConLength_6=ConLength_6, ConEdit_6 = 2, ConPosX_7=ConPosX_7, ConPosY_7=ConPosY_7, ConPosZ_7=ConPosZ_7, ConLength_7=ConLength_7, ConEdit_7 = 2 DEL 1
